name: Multiple Network
description: Multiple Network is a Web3 Private Acceleration Solution for AI that provides privacy protection and data acceleration services based on P2P and SD-WAN technologies. By aggregating the bandwidth of distributed nodes, it offers anonymous communication and encrypted transmission services. Multiple Network provides higher bandwidth and lower latency, widely used in AI model invocation, search engine interactions, and the encryption and acceleration of large-scale sensitive data, enhancing the efficiency and security of AI model training and inference.
